<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Neue Demo-Anfrage – Kaderblick</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/email.css">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="email-container">
		<div class="email-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #018606 0%, #015504 100%); color: #fff; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
			<h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Neue Demo-Anfrage</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="email-content" style="background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(16,185,129,0.08);">
			<p style="margin-top:0; color: #059669; font-weight: 600;">Hallo,</p>
			<p style="color: #475569;">eine neue Demo-Anfrage ist eingegangen:</p>

			<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0;">
				<tr>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; width: 36%;">Name</td>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #475569;">{{ demoRequest.name }}</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">E-Mail</td>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #475569;"><a href="mailto:{{ demoRequest.email }}" style="color: #059669;">{{ demoRequest.email }}</a></td>
				</tr>
				{% if demoRequest.phone %}
				<tr>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">Telefon</td>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #475569;">{{ demoRequest.phone }}</td>
				</tr>
				{% endif %}
				{% if demoRequest.clubName %}
				<tr>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">Verein</td>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #475569;">{{ demoRequest.clubName }}</td>
				</tr>
				{% endif %}
				{% if demoRequest.league %}
				<tr>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">Liga</td>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #475569;">{{ demoRequest.league }}</td>
				</tr>
				{% endif %}
				{% if demoRequest.ageGroup %}
				<tr>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">Altersgruppe / Team</td>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #475569;">{{ demoRequest.ageGroup }}</td>
				</tr>
				{% endif %}
				{% if demoRequest.message %}
				<tr>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">Kommentar</td>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #475569; white-space: pre-wrap;">{{ demoRequest.message }}</td>
				</tr>
				{% endif %}
				<tr>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">Eingegangen am</td>
					<td style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #475569;">{{ demoRequest.createdAt|date('d.m.Y H:i') }} Uhr</td>
				</tr>
			</table>

			<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
				<a href="{{ adminUrl }}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #018606 0%, #015504 100%); color: #fff; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(16,185,129,0.10);">Anfrage im Admin öffnen</a>
			</div>

			<p style="color: #059669; font-weight: 500;">Sportliche Grüße<br>Dein Kaderblick-Team</p>
		</div>
		<div class="email-footer" style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin-top: 20px;">
			<p style="margin: 0 0 4px 0;">Diese E-Mail wurde automatisch generiert. Bitte antworte nicht darauf.</p>
			<p style="margin: 0;">&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Kaderblick. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
